                                <li><img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/ClassMotor/3.png")" alt="" /><br /><span style="color: #1aaf54; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;"><strong>&Ccedil;&Ouml;ZER</strong></span><br /><br />Hayal Edelim,<br />&Ccedil;evik Olalım,<br />Verimli Olalım,<br /><br /><strong>Yapalım!</strong></li>
